snippet.title: Live Coding: Data Visualization with D3.js
snippet.description:
D3.js https://d3js.org is a GPL3 licensed library for making interactive data visualizations in JavaScript, HTML, and CSS. It has a huge library of graphs and visualizations to choose from. Let's learn how it works and try out a few examples!
